{"title":"Spellbook of lightning","url":"https://nethackwiki.com/wiki/Spellbook_of_lightning","type":"markdown","data":"| [spellbook](/wiki/Spellbook \"Spellbook\") of +   lightning   [![Light green spellbook.png](/images/7/7d/Light_green_spellbook.png)](/wiki/File:Light_green_spellbook.png) |                                                                  |\n| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ---------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Appearance                                                                                                                                                               | [random](/wiki/Randomised_appearance \"Randomised appearance\")    |\n|                                                                                                                                                                          |                                                                  |\n| Base price                                                                                                                                                               | 400 [zm](/wiki/Zorkmid \"Zorkmid\")                                |\n| Weight                                                                                                                                                                   | [50](/wiki/Weight \"Weight\")                                      |\n| Turns to read                                                                                                                                                            | 12                                                               |\n| Ink to write                                                                                                                                                             | [20–39](/wik