ealing ([xplev](/wiki/XL \"XL\")/2+1)d6 damage to non-[shock-resistant](/wiki/Shock_resistance \"Shock resistance\") targets instead of the 6d6 of the wand.\n\nIt can be reflected, but magic resistance doesn't stop it.\n\n## See also\n\n- [Wand of lightning](/wiki/Wand_of_lightning \"Wand of lightning\")\n- [List of SLASH'EM spellbooks](/wiki/Spellcasting_\\(SLASH%27EM\\)#SLASH.27EM_spellbooks \"Spellcasting (SLASH'EM)\")\n\n* *This page is a **[SLASH'EM](/wiki/SLASH%27EM \"SLASH'EM\")** related **[stub](/wiki/Category:SLASH%27EM_stubs \"Category:SLASH'EM stubs\")**. Should you wish to do so, you can contribute by [**expanding this page**.](https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Spellbook_of_lightning\\&action=edit)*\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Spellbook of lightning - NetHack Wiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Spellbook_of_lightning\",\"wgTitle\":\"Spellbook of lightning\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":92879,\"wgRevisionId\":92879,\"wgArticleId\":20686,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"Stubs\",\"SLASH'EM stubs\",\"SLASH'EM items\",\"GruntHack items\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul